    NaturalNumberListAdder

    An extension of the Problem class which imposes a derangement relationship on INaturalNumberList source and INaturalNumberList target.
    NaturalNumberListEqualizer
    Note that for two INaturalNumberLists to be equal, in the sense enforced by this IProblem, means for their contents to be equal.
